oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Monroe, Bill, 1911-1996; Stanley, Ralph; Martin, Jimmy; Monroe, James; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (blue and red on white) announcing James Monroe's Sixth Annual Bicentennial Bluegrass Festival with Bill Monroe, Ralph Stanley, Jimmy Martin, James Monroe, and others at Cosby on July 1, 2, 3, and 4. Poster features Bill Monroe, Ralph Stanley, Jimmy Martin, and James Monroe. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20790.
